Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:28.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.43,0:01:31.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for taking care\Nof my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.85,0:01:35.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sayu...You've grown up...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:36.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:37.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Deputy Director?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.98,0:01:39.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,About the trade between\Nthe chief and the notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:40.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:41.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.82,0:01:44.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll now trade you the notebook...\Nfor Sayu Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.74,0:01:47.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, bring the notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.95,0:01:49.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to Los Angeles,\Nby yourself in two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:52.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you L Number Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:57.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the center of SPK...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.71,0:02:01.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I would be... N.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.42,0:02:04.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,N-? Is he joking?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:09.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But what's with this strange feeling-?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:16.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,N...he's similar...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.27,0:02:19.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This feeling...is like L...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:21.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I wouldn't rely on L...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.36,0:02:26.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That means that the CIA and FBI\Nrely on me rather than L
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.99,0:02:29.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to make their decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:32.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the murder of\Nthe Director of the Japanese NPA
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:34.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,is an unforgivable crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:37.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think there is a possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:40.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that this case could lead\Nto the arrest of Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:43.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I will lend you my full support.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:46.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lead to the arrest of Kira?\NWho does he think he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:48.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This confidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.72,0:02:50.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, L?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.35,0:02:51.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:54.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, after the director was murdered...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:56.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Deputy Director Yagami's daughter\Nwas kidnapped by someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:59.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,who we believe to be the same person\Nwho killed the director.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:01.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They contacted us to make\Na deal in Los Angeles.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:04.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A deal? In exchange for\Nthe notebook, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:06.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:07.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:10.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll gather as many investigators as I can\Nin Los Angeles
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:12.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,without telling them the details...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.41,0:03:15.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And use a satellite to\Nmonitor the L.A. area.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:17.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:21.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you have\Ntotal authority on this, L.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.55,0:03:26.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:28.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We make the decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:32.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But what was that about the Americans\Nnot trusting L anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:38.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, are you sure about leaving\Nthis to a fake L
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.27,0:03:40.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,who hasn't succeeded\Nin catching Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:43.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So much the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:46.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It means that there's a chance\Nwe can take advantage of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.65,0:03:48.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, peoples' lives\Nare our first priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.07,0:03:52.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But as the SPK, our goal is...simply...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.70,0:03:56.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to get the notebook and capture Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:03:59.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:07.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if it costs me my life.\NPlease...just save Sayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.09,0:04:10.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say such foolish things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:13.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be satisfied with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:17.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but do you know how painful it would be\Nfor everyone you'd leave behind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:21.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot die in front of Sayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.44,0:04:25.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You may lose contact with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:29.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So if you ever come across a situation where\Nyou have to make a decision by yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:33.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,do whatever you need to do to\Nmake sure that both you and Sayu live.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.45,0:04:35.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.45,0:04:37.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:41.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.79,0:04:44.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can really go with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:49.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I may need your eyes\Nthis time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:53.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:54.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:57.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to start packing immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:09.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... I can't decide...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:13.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Light...\NWhich do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:31.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If things get bad,\NI'll have to kill Sayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:42.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:45.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go on ahead to Los Angeles\Nand make preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.02,0:05:48.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Ide and the rest of you,\Nplease come after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:53.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take different planes.\NSo just in case, Mr. Aizawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.11,0:05:56.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,will follow my father and ride\Nthe same plane as him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:05:57.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:06:00.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As a disguise,\NI'll cut my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:05.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay everyone, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.73,0:06:28.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:30.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?\NAre you one of the kidnappers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.69,0:06:34.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You will take flight SE333.\NI have your ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.11,0:06:37.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry. It's Gate 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:38.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:41.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A man has intercepted him at Narita!\NShould I arrest him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:44.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Aizawa, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.79,0:06:48.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't do us any good\Nif you arrest him right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:50.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, don't lose sight of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:52.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:55.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Deputy Director got\Non a different flight with that man
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:56.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,than the one\Nhe was supposed to catch...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:06:57.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:00.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- I'm going to get on as a police officer...\N- Calm down, Mr. Aizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:03.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, it will be as bad\Nas if you were discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:04.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where it's going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:07.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:08.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to Los Angeles too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.77,0:07:12.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible, they even have a plane?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:13.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:28.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Flight SE333, Flight SE333,\Ncan you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:29.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You are off course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:34.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Flight SE333,\NI can hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.17,0:07:38.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We are not off course.\NI changed course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.01,0:07:40.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:42.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Are you joking?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:45.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a hijacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:49.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just going to take a little detour\Nand drop off a passenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:52.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can track me by radar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:55.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you do anything to interfere...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:58.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not hesitate to crash this plane\Nand take all the passengers with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:05.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light... I mean, L.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:07.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The plane that the Deputy Director is on\Nhas gone
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:08.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,on a different course than to Los Angeles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:11.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's going to be\Ndropped off somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:12.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably the Deputy Director...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.00,0:08:14.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:17.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I checked the flight crew ahead of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:19.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't anyone suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.05,0:08:23.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The pilot is a veteran of\Nover fifteen years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:25.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no problem with\Nthe co-pilot, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:28.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So the enemy is powerful enough to\Ncontrol even normal people like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:32.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn. I've got no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:38.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Director, this is L. Get me N...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:40.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.78,0:08:43.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,N, I think you know the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:49.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you notify the airlines, police\Nand military not to make a move yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:52.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is L doing? How unreliable...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.17,0:08:55.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right... L.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.09,0:08:57.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll figure out where he'll land...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.84,0:09:00.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and keep surveillance over\Nthe area by satellite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:04.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's anything else we can do,\Nplease let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:09.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this PDA...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:11.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Place the wireless earphone\Nin your ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:21.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami, only you can hear my voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:23.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:27.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who kidnapped\Nyour daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.37,0:09:33.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no interest in the lives\Nof you or your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.29,0:09:37.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At this moment, the only thing\NI want is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.17,0:09:39.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,just the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.30,0:09:45.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do as I say,\NI won't kill either of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:48.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've even arranged\Nan exchange procedure
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:50.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that you'll be satisfied with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:52.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not fight me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:56.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am trading the killer notebook\Nfor my daughter's life
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:58.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,with an unknown person...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.94,0:10:05.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When that time comes,\Nwhat should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.99,0:10:12.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As a police officer...\Nas a human being...as a parent...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.12,0:10:53.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L, we have pinpointed\Nwhere they have landed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.41,0:10:54.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,with our satellite cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:58.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send you footage of\Nwhat we are watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:00.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:03.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:05.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How is he going to make\Nthe exchange there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.36,0:11:25.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You see it, don't you, Yagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.32,0:11:27.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Enter from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.07,0:11:28.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Underground, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.03,0:11:30.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:36.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn. Underground, huh-?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:39.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That means he predicted that\Nthere'd be satellite surveillance...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:42.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can't watch him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:08.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's bulletproof glass. You understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.28,0:12:13.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A certain syndicate used this place\Nup until a few years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:15.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to make shady deals.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.87,0:12:17.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've made some modifications.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:19.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Slide the notebook through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.75,0:12:23.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When you slide it in,\NI'll release this handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:25.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll step back and\Nspin the glass door.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.63,0:12:29.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The notebook will\Nbe passed this way
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:30.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and your daughter that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:34.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't go through with the trade,\NI'll shoot your daughter from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:44.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L, do you have a plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:46.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you really think it's all right
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:50.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to let the notebook fall into the\Nhands of someone you don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:53.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y462, begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:56.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now open the notebook\Nand slide it into...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:59.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the slot in the glass door\Nto the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.71,0:13:08.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn. I'm being set back even further...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.84,0:13:10.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just arrived in L.A.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:11.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not in any situation
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:14.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to be giving orders to the police\Nagencies around the world as L...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:17.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate...the notebook will...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:19.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.35,0:13:22.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right? You're pale...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:24.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, shut up and just do as I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.73,0:13:29.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to take more care than usual\Nin killing the criminals in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:32.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's investigating Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.74,0:13:35.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know something bad\Nwill happen
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:36.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if the punishing gets delayed,\Ndon't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:39.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... But who's "he"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.83,0:13:41.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do as I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.29,0:13:43.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just taking out\Nyour anger on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.13,0:13:52.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can still make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:56.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate,\Nis my only option to kill Sayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:13:59.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.43,0:14:00.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall test the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:03.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Test?!\NYou're going to kill someone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.44,0:14:04.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- That's...\N- Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:07.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't trade\Nwithout testing it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:10.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want\Nyour daughter to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:24.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good-!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.54,0:14:28.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the police know\Nabout this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:30.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't blame Sayu's death on Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:37.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!\NAre you all right, Miller?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:42.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you get when you steal and\Nsell our drugs behind my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.89,0:14:44.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a worthless guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.56,0:14:46.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but this is the first time\Nhe's been useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.73,0:14:49.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y462, the target is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:53.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the notebook is real.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:57.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let go.\NWe'll exchange it for your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:07.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayu...Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:09.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they've been saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:12.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The perpetrator is headed\Nfor a helicopter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:15.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can assume that\Nthat's his means of escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.55,0:15:19.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This means that the notebook\Nwas definitely exchanged.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:26.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't know what\NI'm going to do afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:30.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow their helicopter the best\Nyou can until it lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:33.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let it out of\Nyour satellite's view...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:36.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure give difficult orders easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:39.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll try my best...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:44.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good. We've been tricked, L.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.55,0:15:59.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A missile-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:00.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:03.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one that can't\Nbe tracked by radar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:05.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The notebook is on a missile-?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:15.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The missile's been launched!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:17.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The helicopter or the missile?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:19.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one is the notebook on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:24.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, I'm sure you were watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:26.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I did everything as\Nyou told me perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:29.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.17,0:16:33.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So now my past mistakes\Nwill be wiped clean, right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:36.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll wipe them clean...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:37.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.22,0:16:44.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, the helicopter has...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:45.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.68,0:16:49.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This means that the notebook\Nwas definitely on the missile-!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:51.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The missile can't be tracked-!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.27,0:16:54.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've completely lost sight of the target...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:50.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be difficult\Nto retrieve the missile
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:52.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if it falls in an\Nunpopulated area.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:56.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He should be getting his hands on\Nthe notebook right about now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:18:01.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When he does, I have a good idea\Nof what he'll do first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.99,0:19:08.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.16,0:19:13.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:15.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They got us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:16.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Got you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:17.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.75,0:19:22.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Most of the members of the SPK\Nhave been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.84,0:19:31.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L... you helplessly handed over\Nthe notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.39,0:19:35.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,N... Are you saying that if\Nyou were in command
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.39,0:19:37.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that you wouldn't have\Nhanded it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:42.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, with that kind of preparation,\Nit would have been taken either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:45.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in us quarreling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:50.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's help each other and\Ntell each other what we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:55.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have some idea of who\Nthe culprit may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:20:02.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think a person who goes by\Nthe name Mello is behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.67,0:20:04.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The name...Mello...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:08.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have his photograph and\NI don't know his real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:12.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I only know that until four years ago\Nhe was at an orphanage...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:15.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,called Wammy's House\Nin Winchester, England...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.85,0:20:18.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wammy's House-?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:20.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the institution\NWatari established...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.27,0:20:24.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that Mello is playing\Na game with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:28.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To see who can catch the last boss,\NKira, the fastest...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.54,0:20:42.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Armo Justin...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:45.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Armonia Justin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.34,0:20:51.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to the old man, the king,\Nto report that I lost my notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.47,0:20:53.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but when I described what it looked like...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.68,0:20:58.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he said that Ryuk said it was his and\Nthat he dropped it, and took it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:02.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do in this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:06.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In this case, you've got to\Nget it back from Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:08.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.78,0:21:13.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I have to...\Ngo the Human world, huh-?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.28,0:21:16.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...you have to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:18.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:39.85,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}This single page Forever depressing
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:42.23,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A fleeting tactic in the eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.15,0:21:46.98,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Without petition evil against the law\Nchain it in prison
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:49.57,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Poison the notebook fear the lust
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:52.28,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Delusion of being deceived\Nperpetually drooling
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.36,0:21:54.91,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Judgement is "crime control" they driveled
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.08,0:21:57.54,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Who has the Rx for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:22:00.25,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A decriminalized world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.33,0:22:03.17,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A sanctioned word
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.21,0:22:07.09,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Taking in heat\NJust like "Pirates of Death"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.50,0:22:10.63,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Atone with the game of laws\NBilly in despair
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.67,0:22:13.43,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Now, it's time for ethics\NNow, the unstoppable Eraser Rain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.18,0:22:16.05,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Billy in despair
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:18.60,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Now, it's time for ethics\NNow, the unstoppable Eraser Rain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.68,0:22:21.81,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The unstoppable Eraser Rain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.24,0:22:36.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please calm down and listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.16,0:22:41.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On November 10, 23:59,\Nall the Mafia will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.21,0:22:46.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This moment is your best chance\Nto get back the notebook.
